Vom Filmset ins echte Leben, Sergio Klee und Christian Wei√üe sprechen √ºber Sicherheit, Wahrnehmung und Setkultur 

Wenn Ver√§nderung den Blick sch√§rft 

In diesem Teil erz√§hlt Sergio Klee, wie pers√∂nliche Entwicklung die eigene Pr√§senz am Set ver√§ndert. Er beschreibt, wie innere Anspannung weicht, wenn man versteht, woher Nervosit√§t wirklich kommt. Durch die Reflexion seines eigenen Weges zeigt er, wie Selbstkritik lauter sein kann als jedes Lob und weshalb Sicherheit erst entsteht, wenn man sich selbst erkennt statt sich zu verstecken. 

Wahrnehmung, Ego und die Kunst, nichts pers√∂nlich zu nehmen 

Sergio schildert eine Situation, in der er an einem Set offen √§u√üerte, wo er sich wohlf√ºhlt, und pl√∂tzlich in kritische Blicke lief. Er erkl√§rt, wie schnell Menschen neutrale Aussagen bewerten und warum das Ego immer eine Wertung sucht, auch wenn keine da ist. 

Von Atmosph√§re, Respekt und Kleinigkeiten mit grosser Wirkung 

Die Episode zeigt, wie unterschiedlich Drehtage wirken k√∂nnen. Sergio vergleicht Setkulturen, Catering, Umgangsformen und kleine Gesten, die den Unterschied zwischen distanziert und famili√§r ausmachen. Seine Erfahrungen bei Formaten wie K√∂ln 50667, Alles was z√§hlt, Barbara Salesch und Ulrich Wetzel machen deutlich, wie stark Wertsch√§tzung das eigene Gef√ºhl von Zugeh√∂rigkeit pr√§gt und warum sich manche Orte sofort richtig anf√ºhlen. 

Reinwachsen in Abl√§ufe und R√§ume, bis die Kamera l√§uft 

Sergio beschreibt, wie man bei jedem neuen Projekt zuerst fremd wirkt, dann Orientierung findet und schlie√ülich ankommt. Vom ersten Guten Tag im B√ºro √ºber Kost√ºm und Maske bis zur laufenden Kamera zeigt er, wie viel Sicherheit in Wiederholung und Vorbereitung steckt. Das Gespr√§ch √∂ffnet einen seltenen Einblick in die leisen Momente vor dem Take, in denen man begreift, dass man dazugeh√∂rt. 

Zu mir, Christian Wei√üe 

Ich bin Christian Wei√üe, Medienunternehmer, Content Creator und Inhaber der Karrideo Image- und Eventfilmproduktion aus K√∂ln. Ich entwickle Bewegtbildformate, erz√§hle Geschichten f√ºr Unternehmen, Organisationen und Pers√∂nlichkeiten und kenne als Darsteller beide Seiten der Kamera. 

Abonniere den Kanal, like das Video, teile deine Gedanken in den Kommentaren und besuche mind_body_coach_ auf Instagram f√ºr weitere Impulse von Sergio Klee.

Hallo Zusammen,

mein Name ist Willi, ich bin 30 Jahre alt, arbeite als Senior Management Consultant bei einer internationalen Steuerberatungs- und Wirtschaftspr√ºfungsgesellschaft, bin nebenbei Unternehmer ‚Äì und trage seit meiner Kindheit eine gro√üe Leidenschaft in mir: Film & Schauspiel.

Schon damals haben mich Geschichten, komplexe Charaktere und starke Bilder fasziniert. W√§hrend meines Studiums durfte ich bereits an einem Independent-Filmprojekt mitwirken, und dieses Feuer ist √ºber die Jahre immer gr√∂√üer geworden. Jetzt ist f√ºr mich der Zeitpunkt gekommen, mich vor der Kamera auszuprobieren und diesen Weg zu verfolgen.

Ich beginne aktuell mit hochwertigem Schauspielunterricht, unter anderem bei Lehrern, die an renommierten Universit√§ten in den USA ausgebildet wurden.

Ich liebe es, mich tief in Rollen hineinzudenken, Charaktere authentisch umzusetzen und sie exzellent performen zu lassen. Hierbei bin ich sehr selbstkritisch, reflektierend, detailverliebt und habe hohe Anspr√ºche an mich selbst. Auch f√ºr Szenenbild und Atmosph√§re habe ich ein gutes Gesp√ºr ‚Äì ich gehe vollkommen in kreativer Arbeit auf.

Daher w√ºrde ich mich sehr freuen, in spannenden Projekten mitzuwirken ‚Äì gerne auch No-Budget und in ‚ÄûNebenrollen‚Äú, denn das ist meine gro√üe Leidenschaft.

Wenn ihr Unterst√ºtzung sucht, meldet euch sehr gerne bei mir. Ich freue mich auf den Austausch und darauf, gemeinsam Geschichten zum Leben zu erwecken.

Beste Gr√º√üe,

Willi

PURPLE DREAMS PRODUCTIONS are looking for several performers to join a few projects, primarily our brand new family-friendly play: 

THE PRINCESS & THE KNIGHT

a fantasy play written by Tobias Nicholls

Welcome to Twinklewood, a fantastical land where darkness and light have lived in harmony for decades‚Ä¶ until now.

Whilst the King is away on a royal tour, the Ruler of the Shadow Realm makes an unexpected appearance. Sir Milo is determined to keep his princess safe, but with her Kingdom thrown into chaos, Princess Nova - who has long dreamt of adventure - springs into action, taking them on a journey up to the highest mountain and down to the deepest, darkest cave.

Battles are fought and lessons learned on this funny and exciting quest.  

This brand new production is set to debut at The Seagull Theatre in Lowestoft on Saturday 4th April 2026

Two performances on the one day as a tester before we look at booking any others. 

The script is currently going through a rewrite, with the intention to have the cast help to develop the characters through the rehearsal process with the director. 

Adding to the fantastical nature of the story, the characters of Twinklewood will all feature likenesses to animals - realised through costume and make-up.  Aside from one, roles have not been assigned any particular animal, allowing the chosen actors can help build their character.

Payment: at this stage of development it‚Äôs best to consider this a profit share, although this could change to a flat fee - happy to have open and honest discussions with applicants. 

Rehearsals will take place at our studio in Hunstanton (PE36), and will be as flexible as possible to fit around other commitments.

If you are interested, or know someone that might be, please get in touch via a DM on here, or email purple-dreams@hotmail.co.uk

Candidates with the ability to sing would be favourable.'

He potentially has a romantic interest in Lotti. This role may include fight and and dance choreography as is present during these scenes.'

This role may include fight and dance choreography as IS present during these scenes.'

A supporting role as she is left behind SO misses the adventure itself. She claims to be magical and has andhas a magical ball. Thisrole has room for expansionif candidates have experience with simple magic tricks but don't let that element put you off as that would be a bonus rather than integral.'

üé¨ CASTING CALL | PAID CAMPAIGN | 'TWO NEEDS, ONE PLAN' üé¨

Hi everyone,

We are currently casting for a small, warm and family-oriented campaign titled ‚ÄúTwo Needs, One Plan‚Äù and are looking for a South Asian / Indian male actor, aged 60‚Äì75, to play the role of a Grandfather.

Role: Grandfather
Age: 60‚Äì75
Ethnicity: South Asian / Indian
Vibe: Warm, expressive, natural presence
Shoot: 1 day in or around Bedfordshire, Hertfordshire, or London (Date TBC ‚Äì ideally December 2025)
Fee: ¬£175 ‚Äì ¬£200 (flat fee)

Includes:
‚úÖ Reasonable travel expenses will be reimbursed, with mileage calculated using the fuel cost calculator from [FleetNews.co.uk](http://fleetnews.co.uk/) (UK average Pence per litre), or equivalent public transport fares.
‚úÖ Food will be provided during shoot hours.
‚úÖ Professional production

Company will possess unlimited usage rights across all platforms.

If you fit the brief, or know someone who does, please send the following to [michelle@universaltvmedia.com](mailto:michelle@universaltvmedia.com):
* Headshot
* Showreel, online professional profile, or previous work
* Current available & unavailable dates in December
* Confirmation of day rate within the stated range
* Your email and phone number

Please feel free to tag or share with actors in your network who might be interested.

We look forward to seeing your submissions and collaborating with talented performers from this community!

#castingcalls #asianactors #ukactors #paidgigs #casting #southasianactors #actoropportunity

Join us and grow together in the fastest-rising livestream e-commerce market in North America!

üé¨ Job Responsibilities:
 ‚Ä¢ Host livestream shows on the Whatnot platform to showcase and sell products (categories depend on the store such as fashion/beauty/collectibles/home goods, etc.)
 ‚Ä¢ Prepare product scripts and selling points before each show; assist in improving livestream procedures
 ‚Ä¢ Interact with viewers, answer questions, and create an engaging atmosphere to increase conversion
 ‚Ä¢ Work with the team on livestream reviews and traffic optimization

‚ú® We‚Äôre Looking for Someone Who:
 ‚Ä¢ Has livestreaming experience (any platform such as TikTok / YouTube / IG Live, etc.)
 ‚Ä¢ Outgoing, energetic, and enjoys engaging with people
 ‚Ä¢ Has good image and strong on-camera presence
 ‚Ä¢ Is fluent in spoken English and capable of hosting in English
 ‚Ä¢ Is eager to learn and grow in the livestream e-commerce industry
 ‚Ä¢ Is legally eligible to work in the U.S.

üìç Location:
Los Angeles (Remote or On-site depending on position needs)

‚è± Schedule:
3‚Äì6 livestream sessions per week; flexible hours negotiable

üí∞ Compensation:
Base salary + Performance commission + Bonuses
High performers enjoy rapid growth and unlimited income potential!

üéØ Preferred Qualifications (Not Required):

 ‚Ä¢ Skills in video editing, content planning, and streaming metrics to showcase

üì© How to Apply:
Please send your resume + a short self-introduction video and/or previous livestream links to:
hzhong@thunderex.com
Email subject: Whatnot Host + Your Name

SHARING PAID OPPORTUNITY 

I‚Äôm Jude, casting with Liz Lewis Casting Partners, and I wanted to share a current project we‚Äôre working on for Metamucil.

For this particular project, we are actually looking for real Metamucil users, ages 45‚Äì60, with no professional acting or performing experience. While we know this community is full of talented actors, we wanted to share here in case you might know friends, family members, or people in your network who could be a great fit.

It‚Äôs a nationwide search. The shoot location is still being finalized and may be Austin, or possibly Mexico or Canada. If travel is required, production will cover all travel and accommodations.

Compensation is $500 per shoot day, plus $3,400 for 1-year usage, all media.

**Participants cannot have any professional performing experience, including paid acting, dancing, or singing work (union or non-union). **

To submit please click on this link [Metamucil Form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSffQ4Zl_-5Evj8FE5NNi9aTaYuc-htYG1gLG25xmTIcI_CM4g/viewform?usp=header)

If this sounds like you or someone you know, feel free to reach out or share!

items.text:
CASTING CALL ‚Äì STARFARM 

We‚Äôre casting fun, stylish young women (15‚Äì25) for an unscripted eco-reality series!

AI is taking over the world. Replacing jobs, replacing people, reforming industries. They are humanity's greatest creation yet our ultimate competition. Now, an unscripted eco-reality series featuring 10 young women, learning to live on a completely remote and self-sustainable farm - across the dirt road, lies another self-sustained farm; run by AI. Will they survive or thrive? Will they change the future for the next generation of girls, by proving something woman-powered can be more fruitful than something AI-powered?

Do you have :
* 
**STRONG SENSE OF PERSONAL STYLE AND CREATIVE CONFIDENCE**
* 
**PASSION FOR FASHION, ART, FILM, TV, MUSIC VIDEOS OR DIGITAL CONTENT**
* 
**LOVE FOR ANIMALS, OR AN INTEREST IN SOCIAL/ENVIRONMENTAL CAUSES**

Think: The Simple Life x Ready Player One

Filming in BAY AREA, remote filming roles open too

Nationwide applicants encouraged to apply (travel & accommodations provided).

Total Pay: US$1,750 (est. 5 days of work)

TO APPLY:

Email themadelynx@gmail.com

Subject: *STAR FARM ‚Äì Your Name, Age*

Include: Name, age, location + recent photo (headshots appreciated, not required) + short intro.

New dates added - Dec 8-19 in Las Vegas. To book go to https://rebrand.ly/freehdsht

FREE HEADSHOT and 1-HOUR SESSION ‚Äì East Summerlin, Las Vegas

Address sent automatically after booking

Hi! I‚Äôm Steve Fogarty, a Las Vegas headshot specialist and owner of EXPO TRAFFIC, where we run large-scale headshot activations for major trade shows (600-700 people over 2.5 days).

I‚Äôm currently testing new lighting setups and posing flows for upcoming conventions, and I‚Äôm looking for real people to sit for practice sessions in a more relaxed environment. In return for your time, you get a full headshot session and one professional, retouched headshot for free.

**What You Get**
* A 60‚Äì75 minute headshot session
* Multiple looks + lighting setups
* A private online gallery
* One edited, retouched image included
* Additional images optional (zero pressure)

**Examples of my retouching**

[https://rebrand.ly/retouching](https://rebrand.ly/retouching)

Why There‚Äôs a $20 Fee

It‚Äôs not a sales charge. It‚Äôs a **non-refundable security deposit and show-up guarantee** that ensures the schedule stays reliable for both of us. The $20 simply confirms your commitment to attend ‚Äî and your favorite image is still included for free.

How You Get Your Image

After the session:
* We will review your images, and you'll tell me which ones are your favorites that you do not want deleted.
* I will edit and retouch your favorites, then upload them to your private gallery.
* You can download your favorite image using a coupon code (provided).
* You‚Äôre welcome to purchase extras, but it‚Äôs totally optional.

What to Expect / How to Prepare
* Arrive camera-ready (mirror + restroom available)
* Plan for 3‚Äì4 different looks
* Avoid pure white tops if possible
* Relax ‚Äî I‚Äôll guide you through every pose and expression

Safety + Professionalism
* All public areas are video security-monitored for your comfort and safety
* Private areas (bathrooms, changing areas) are never recorded
* References available by request

You can preview my work here:

[https://www.expotraffic.com/headshots/las-vegas-headshots](https://www.expotraffic.com/headshots/las-vegas-headshots)

**Location**

**East Summerlin near Rainbow & Alta**

**Exact address provided after booking.**

**Looking forward to creating something great together!**

**‚Äì Steve Fogarty**

**Owner ‚Äì STEVEN JOSEPH PHOTOGRAPHY | EXPO TRAFFIC HEADSHOTS**

+++EXKLUSIVER SCHAUSPIEL-WORKSHOP f√ºr QUEREINSTEIGER*INNEN+++

(NUR NOCH 3 FREIE PL√ÑTZE! - Stand: 06.12.2025)

#schauspielworkshop #quereinsteiger #schauspielquereinsteiger #quereinsteigerworkshop #cameraacting #arbeitsworkshop #showreel #aboutme #film #tv #exklusiv #engelspostmanagement

Aufgrund der gro√üen Nachfrage veranstalte ich im JANUAR 2026 (09.-11.01.+16.-18.01.2026 / 2 WE) einen EXKLUSIVEN, 6-T√ÑGIGEN Schauspiel-Workshop f√ºr QUEREINSTEIGER*INNEN. Die Inhalte k√∂nnt Ihr dem Flyer entnehmen. 

Quereinsteiger*innen haben wenig M√∂glichkeiten auf dem deutschen Markt, weshalb ich mich dazu entschieden habe, ein sinnvolles, n√ºtzliches Angebot auf den Markt zu bringen. 

Es handelt sich um einen PRAXISORIENTIERTEN Workshop, was bedeutet, in welchem mit den Teilnehmenden an der Performance gearbeitet wird, u. a. durch Szenenarbeit, E-/Live-Casting-Situationen, Camera-Acting etc. Au√üerdem erhalten die Teilnehmenden alle wichtigen Informationen rund um das Thema "Selbstmarketing" - zusammen mit wertvollen Tipps und Tricks. 

Zus√§tzlich produzieren wir eine professionelle SHOWREELSZENE f√ºr jeden Teilnehmenden, welche wir in dem 6-t√§gigen Workshop vorbereiten (*WICHTIGE INFO: Die Produktion der Szenen findet au√üerhalb des Workshops statt. üéÑ‚ú® What can a small team create when human imagination meets AI?

Over the past few weeks, we‚Äôve been working with a small creative team on something that started as a simple experiment‚Ä¶ and grew into a full multi-genre music video collection called "The Hope Multiverse - Vol. 1."

Every video began with a human idea, emotion, or story we wanted to express.

AI helped us bring those ideas to life in cinematic, playful, and sometimes totally unexpected ways.

A fun twist for early December:
Two of the favorites so far are Christmas songs - one ‚Äúsung‚Äù by a baby, and one performed by an original AI pop singer. Both somehow feel warm, joyful, and surprisingly human.

The playlist spans an entire mini-universe of concepts:

 üé® Van Gogh‚Äôs self-portrait singing an art-inspired ballad

 üåô An anime girl finding calm after digital burnout

 üõ∏ A UFO satire teasing ‚Äúnothing to see here‚Äù secrecy

 üê¶ A real backyard bird inspiring a song about courage

 üîß A kid inventor‚Äôs chaotic (and heartfelt) pop anthem

All of this came from a small team exploring one question I care deeply about: What happens when humans lead the creative vision - and AI expands what‚Äôs possible?

And just to be clear:
We aren‚Äôt associated with any AI platforms.

If you‚Äôre curious how storytelling is evolving - or if you want some early-December holiday spirit - I‚Äôd love for you to explore the playlist and read the video descriptions. Each one explains how the idea started, how the visuals and music came together, and how human creativity guided the entire process.

Would love to hear which piece surprises you the most. üéß‚ú®

üëâ Watch the 12 music videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX6tC4WGOeiMwZAZTEh-1UCyMhscLfD0W

items.text:
Just wondering where do people usually find acting extras jobs? 
I'm wanting to get into the industry and being an extra seems the best way but im not sure actually how to get started. 
Would love some advice üòäüòä

topComments.text: An actor/actress and an extra are two totally different jobs.

If you are interested in acting rather than SA work,  I recommend getting hold of a copy of Actors and Performers Yearbook which gives a good brief overview of the profession and helps to explain how industry casting works and who does what.  

There is very rarely a "progression" from SA work to acting work as actors and extras are engaged differently.

If you do want extra/SA work then joining extras agencies is the way to go.  

There's an SA Facebook group called Heavy Pencil for SAs which you may find interesting.  

Casting Collective (and a number of other agencies) have some fairly comprehensive information on their websites about extra work.

At ùêåùêöùê´ùêõùê•ùêû ùêÄùêúùêöùêùùêûùê¶ùê≤ ùê¢ùêß ùêíùê∞ùê¢ùêßùê≠ùê®ùêß, ùêåùêöùêßùêúùê°ùêûùê¨ùê≠ùêûùê´, we don‚Äôt just run drama classes ‚Äì we train serious, committed actors for real careers in film, TV and theatre.
We are a multi-award-winning drama academy, proudly holding both the ùêåùêöùêßùêúùê°ùêûùê¨ùê≠ùêûùê´ & ùêçùê®ùê´ùê≠ùê° ùêñùêûùê¨ùê≠ ùêèùê´ùêûùê¨ùê≠ùê¢ùê†ùêû ùêÄùê∞ùêöùê´ùêù ùêüùê®ùê´ ùêÉùê´ùêöùê¶ùêö ùêíùêúùê°ùê®ùê®ùê• ùê®ùêü ùê≠ùê°ùêû ùêòùêûùêöùê´ ùüêùüéùüêùüì/ùüêùüî and the ùêÑùüê ùêåùêûùêùùê¢ùêö ùêÄùê∞ùêöùê´ùêù ùêüùê®ùê´ ùêÅùêûùê¨ùê≠ ùêÉùê´ùêöùê¶ùêö ùêíùêúùê°ùê®ùê®ùê• ùê®ùêü ùê≠ùê°ùêû ùêòùêûùêöùê´ ùüêùüéùüêùüì/ùüêùüî, as well as being a ùêîùêä ùêíùê¶ùêöùê•ùê• ùêÅùêÆùê¨ùê¢ùêßùêûùê¨ùê¨ ùêÄùê∞ùêöùê´ùêùùê¨ ùüêùüéùüêùüì finalist, representing Manchester in the ùêÅùêûùê¨ùê≠ ùêíùê¶ùêöùê•ùê• ùêÅùêÆùê¨ùê¢ùêßùêûùê¨ùê¨ category.
We‚Äôre also recognised by ùêíùê©ùê®ùê≠ùê•ùê¢ùê†ùê°ùê≠, the UK‚Äôs leading casting platform, for our professional standard of training.
_____________________________________________________

ùêìùê´ùêöùê¢ùêßùê¢ùêßùê† ùêìùê°ùêöùê≠ ùêÄùêúùê≠ùêÆùêöùê•ùê•ùê≤ ùêÅùêÆùê¢ùê•ùêùùê¨ ùêÇùêöùê´ùêûùêûùê´ùê¨:

At Marble Academy, you don‚Äôt just ‚Äúdo drama classes‚Äù ‚Äì you train like a working actor.
Under award-winning tutor Christian Le Feuvre, you‚Äôll focus on:
‚Ä¢ ùêíùêúùê´ùê¢ùê©ùê≠ & ùê¨ùêúùêûùêßùêû ùê∞ùê®ùê´ùê§ ‚Äì breaking down text like a pro
‚Ä¢ ùêÄùêÆùêùùê¢ùê≠ùê¢ùê®ùêß ùê≠ùêûùêúùê°ùêßùê¢ùê™ùêÆùêû ‚Äì self-tapes and in-room auditions that stand out
‚Ä¢ ùêÇùê°ùêöùê´ùêöùêúùê≠ùêûùê´ & ùêûùê¶ùê®ùê≠ùê¢ùê®ùêß ‚Äì truthful, layered performances
‚Ä¢ ùêéùêß-ùêúùêöùê¶ùêûùê´ùêö ùê¨ùê§ùê¢ùê•ùê•ùê¨ ‚Äì marks, continuity and confidence
‚Ä¢ Professional mindset ‚Äì how real actors work, prepare and behave.

You‚Äôll not only improve the talent you already have ‚Äì you‚Äôll unlearn bad habits, stop doing the things that hold so many actors back, and replace them with sharp, reliable technique.

Whether you‚Äôre just starting or ready to level up, this is where you turn ‚ÄúI‚Äôd love to act‚Äù into ‚ÄúI‚Äôm building a real career.‚Äù
_______________________________________________________

ùêåùê®ùê´ùêû ùêìùê°ùêöùêß ùêö ùêÇùê•ùêöùê¨ùê¨: ùêÄ ùêÇùê´ùêûùêöùê≠ùê¢ùêØùêû ùêáùêÆùêõ:

That‚Äôs not all‚ÄîMarble Academy produce award-winning films, hosts interactive workshops, extremely popular networking events for actors and filmmakers, and provides invaluable casting opportunities for our students. We take immense pride in the accomplishments of our graduates, many of whom have gone on to star in acclaimed projects.
______________________________________________________

ùêÄùêÆùêùùê¢ùê≠ùê¢ùê®ùêß & ùêÑùêßùê´ùê®ùê• ùêüùê®ùê´ ùüêùüéùüêùüî:

If you‚Äôre ready to take your craft seriously:
1. Visit [www.marbleacademy.co.uk](https://www.marbleacademy.co.uk)
2. Check out all the information and read our reviews
3. Apply for an audition and make 2026 the year you stop ‚Äúthinking about it‚Äù and actually do something for your future as an actor.
___________________________________________________

please email your headshot and resume to theatre@xoxotv.ca to be scheduled with an audition time, or to request a self-tape submission.

character breakdowns can be found in our ‚Äúaudition package‚Äù link in bio.

We are casting for the 2026 Weird and Wonderful festival which will run between March 3rd and March 8th.

‚ÄúSardines‚Äù follows five sardines as they bicker over life's meaning and their purpose in the world. 

We are looking for 5 actors of any age or look who can comfortably play off of each others comedic timing.

If you are interested in auditioning for a role please send a self tape that you feel fits the criteria via we transfer / any other downloadable link to:

Seanrobinsonfreelance@gmail.com

Self tapes are due by 31st December and the cast will be contacted by the new year.

Please note: this is a 20 min play and will be part of a three play evening. A profit share will be paid.

items.text:
Hallo liebe Freunde der Musik

Am 05.12.2025 erscheint unser Song HIMMEL AUF ERDEN auf Spotify und allen anderen Musik-Streaming-Platformen.

H√∂rt gerne mal rein, erz√§hlt es weiter und rockt das Sofa.

Himmel auf Erden 

Du warst der Himmel auf Erden, ich der Regen, der verwirrt auf uns f√§llt.

Eine Liebe, die nicht verstanden, auf wunderbare Weise gelebt und ausradiert wird.

Dieser Rocksong symbolisiert eine Reise durch H√∂hen und Tiefen, mal laut, mal leise,

vom Winde verweht, in Gedanken versunken, intensiv gelebt, nehme ich dich mit... pack den Rucksack voller Erinnerung und komm mit!

 Eure DiMiKA CRUNCH-POP¬Æ

items.text:
**Casting Call for a 20-min short**

Hi everyone! We‚Äôre looking for non-union actors who are based on Vancouver, BC. We're thrilled to have new blood in our team! 

**Production Information: **

-Location: Vancouver, BC

-Shoot Dates: Jan 3rd-4th.

-Genre:Drama, Thriller

-Non-Union/Volunteer

-Crafty+IMDb credit provided 

**Roles: **

**Officer Shaw Male 28-50**

A true believer in justice and law enforcement. He doesn‚Äôt believe mentalism is anything more than cheap party tricks, but he finds Chaz and his shtick entertaining, so he allows Chaz to perform for him and explain himself. With every word Chaz says in his defence, Officer Shaw starts to see through Chaz‚Äôs persona and eventually confronts him about the moral, ethical and legal complications his profession entails. The conversation reaches a boiling point when Chaz attempts to read Officer Shaw‚Äôs mind by repeating the last words spoken to Shaw from his missing daughter.

**Mark Male 28-50**

A bitter, cynical man whose sole goal is to prove that Chaz and everything he stands for is a complete pile of crap. He questions everything, every small movement, every word Chaz says, he does not let anything slip. He is the worst participant a magician could possibly ask for. He believes that Chaz is exploiting people, lying to them about magical abilities in order to profit from manipulating the public‚Äôs belief. Nothing Chaz says or does can change his mind and he will stop at nothing to embarrass Chaz live on air and prove that Chaz is a complete fraud.

**Kayla Female 18-30**

Mark‚Äôs na√Øve podcast co-host. She is fascinated with the idea and concept of mentalism and thinks Chaz‚Äôs persona is incredibly exciting. She represents the average person obsessed with magic and mentalism. She loves tricks being performed on her and believes it‚Äôs all harmless

fun. She doesn‚Äôt see anything wrong with what Chaz is doing and truly believes he can read her mind. She tries to keep the order as Mark and Chaz scream at each other, simply wanting to have a fun time and create an entertaining show for her audience.

**To submit:**

Please submit headshot and demo reel to **theartofreadingminds.short@gmail.com** and indicate which role you‚Äôd like to be considered for.

S√òGES: To kvindelige vennepar (Alder 45-50) til reklameoptagelse om vinterbadning ‚Äì Betalt job (Vejle omr√•det) 

Hej allesammen!
Jeg er i gang med at udvikle en reklamefilm til sociale medier for et nyt vinterbadeprojekt. Jeg har filmet annoncer f√∏r, men det er f√∏rste gang jeg leder efter ‚Äúskuespillere‚Äù, s√• jeg h√•ber virkelig p√• at finde et par gode matches her i gruppen.

Hvem s√∏ger jeg?
Jeg leder efter to kvinder i alderen 45-55, som i forvejen er venner, og allerhelst et vennepar der allerede vinterbader sammen.

K√¶mpe plus hvis I har et favoritspot ved Vejle Fjord, som vi evt. kan filme ved. (Ellers s√• har jeg et sted klar)
I m√• meget gerne v√¶re fra Vejle og omegn, s√• vi slipper for lang transport.

Hvad g√•r optagelsen ud p√•?
Reklamen bliver et naturligt, siddende interview, hvor I har en afslappet samtale om jeres oplevelser med vinterbadning ‚Äì hvad det giver jer, hvorfor I g√∏r det, og hvad f√¶llesskabet betyder.

Derudover filmer vi lidt B-roll (sm√• stemningsklip der bliver lagt ovenp√• interviewets lyd), fx:
‚Äì I vinterbader
‚Äì I hygger, griner, snakker
‚Äì I g√•r p√• broen
‚Äì Close-ups af detaljer (h√•ndkl√¶der, damp, fjorden osv.)

Til sidst laver vi ogs√• et kort klip hvor I er i vandet, s√• badedragt er n√∏dvendigt.

Jeg s√∏rger for:

‚Ä¢ Morgenk√•ber (m√• gerne selv medbringes, hvis I har)

‚Ä¢ Kaffe/te

‚Ä¢ Et hyggeligt setup

Det vil v√¶re smart at have lidt varmere t√∏j under morgenk√•ben, da vi selvf√∏lgelig filmer udend√∏rs.

Varighed & betaling:
Optagelserne tager ca. 2 timer. - Jeg sigter efter at vi kan g√∏re det p√• Fredag d. 12/12, da vejret lige nu ser bedst ud der! Vi kan aftale n√¶rmere tidspunkt, men selvf√∏lgelig i dagslys. (Ellers m√• det blive l√∏rdag, hvis jeres arbejde er en tidsm√¶ssig udfordring)

Jeg leder efter to kvinder i alderen 45-55, som i forvejen er venner, og allerhelst et vennepar der allerede vinterbader sammen.

Die neue Essenz-Methode ist nicht einfach eine weitere Schauspieltechnik. 

 

Die Methode basiert auf:
* 15+ Jahren Casting- & Kamera-Erfahrung
* Coaching von hunderten Darstellern
* Erfolgen, die Menschen in Filme, Serien, Preise & Chart-Songs gebracht haben

 

Sie vereint alles, was du wirklich brauchst um vor der Kamera zu strahlen. 

Strukturiert, gegliedert und direkt umsetzbar. 

 

Im Workshop lernst du:

‚úî wie du Energie vor der Kamera aufbaust

‚úî wie du ber√ºhrst statt spielst

‚úî wie du Blockaden l√∂st

‚úî wie du dich authentisch zeigst

‚úî wie du deine Wirkung nutzt, um Caster und Regisseure WIRKLICH zu √ºberzeugen. 

 

üìÜ **Early Bird gilt nur noch bis 10.12, 23:59 Uhr. **

üí¨ **Kommentiere ESSENZ**, wenn du den Link willst.
